Patch 8.0.0024
Problem:    When the netbeans channel closes, "DETACH" is put in the output
            part. (Ozaki Kiichi)
Solution:   Write "DETACH" in the socket part.
Files:      src/channel.c, src/testdir/test_netbeans.vim


