Patch 8.0.0026
Problem:    Error format with %W, %C and %Z does not work. (Gerd Wachsmuth)
Solution:   Skip code when qf_multiignore is set. (Lcd)
Files:      src/quickfix.c, src/testdir/test_quickfix.vim


