Patch 8.0.0092
Problem:    C indenting does not support nested namespaces that C++ 17 has.
Solution:   Add check that passes double colon inside a name. (Pauli, closes
            #1214)
Files:      src/misc1.c, src/testdir/test3.in, src/testdir/test3.ok


